HEADWORD: Modernization
<hw>Mod`ern*i*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
rendering modern in style; the act or process of causing to conform to
modern of thinking or acting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

